Usage

compute_ellipse_area(
  data,
  CoPX_col,
  CoPY_col,
  ID,
  time_col = NULL,
  epoch_length = NULL,
  confint = 0.95
)

Arguments

data

a data frame containing postural data (i.e., Center of pressure displacements on both the antero-posterior and medio-lateral axis)

CoPX_col

a column from the data frame storing center of pressure displacements on the medio-lateral axis

CoPY_col

a column from the data frame storing center of pressure displacements on the antero-posterior axis

ID

a column from the data frame storing unique identifiers for each participant/session

time_col

a column from the data frame storing time course over the session (optional; for computing results synthetised per epochs)

epoch_length

an optional argument (if computing results synthetised at an epoch level) specifying length of the desired epoch

confint

desired percentage for the confidence in the ellipse area (default is .95)

Value

a data frame with an additional 'ellipse_area' column
